{"tid":2217102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方不知便衣身份：警唔記得","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T07:53:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fabe69a11884b242425db6100b86907c531dd980","tid":2217102,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/ZSFU6C5ZEVGTNP7DBVDHENN3II/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FZSFU6C5ZEVGTNP7DBVDHENN3II%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=e4da802a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FZSFU6C5ZEVGTNP7DBVDHENN3II%2F&h=d1cdf3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/ZSFU6C5ZEVGTNP7DBVDHENN3II/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n控方不知便衣身份：警唔記得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z_-LmiVnkloXtGBuLh3yyXlF7zc=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TSR3QHJDDFHDXCSQIJFIOIPWTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz_-LmiVnkloXtGBuLh3yyXlF7zc%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTSR3QHJDDFHDXCSQIJFIOIPWTY.jpg&h=7601778b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳應武<br />\n<br />\n【拒捕案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年6.12在金鐘中彈的退休漢「老吳」吳應武，今年1月身處旺角堵路現場，遭警員制服期間涉揮臂抗拒，被控拒捕罪，尚待答辯。辯方昨要求控方披露有份制服老吳的便衣警身份，惟控方指，案中防暴警稱當日有「太多」便衣同袍，「唔記得係邊一位」。辯方無奈表示無法追查，裁判官則稱：「佢哋（警方）講嘅嘢真定假，就另一回事啦，可以審訊時處理。」<br />\n<br />\n被告吳應武（58歲）被控今年1月19日在旺角「潮流特區」外抗拒警員22266。辯方大律師黃宇逸昨稱，現時只知涉事者包括警員22266及警長51624；辯方上月起三度去信律政司，要求披露第三名有份制服被告的便衣警身份，但一直無回音，直至開庭前才獲控方口頭回覆表明拒絕提供資料，故要求法庭下令控方披露。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官建議審訊時盤問<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。辯方無奈表示「冇辦法追落去」。主任裁判官羅德泉則建議辯方在審訊時透過盤問處理。<br />\n<br />\n辯方另要求控方披露現場推進隊伍全部37名警員的記事冊，以及調查人員曾在警方內部系統檢閱的當日片段。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC2375/20"}]}